Definition: any shrub or small tree of the genus Tamarix having small scalelike or needle-shaped leaves and feathery racemes of small white or pinkish flowers
Example: of mostly coastal areas with saline soil
Synonyms: shrub, genus_Tamarix, m, any, or, small, tree, of, the, genus, Tamarix, having, scalelike, needle-shaped, leaves, and, feathery, racemes, white, pinkish, flowers, mostly, coastal, areas, with, saline, soil
Category: noun.plant
